</div>
<div>
<p>
<term>禦史</term>
<persName>陳薦</persName>疏<pc>：</pc>
<pc>“</pc>
<quote>
<name key="李定" type="givenName">定</name>頃為涇縣主簿<pc>，</pc>聞庶母<persName>仇</persName>氏死<pc>，</pc>匿不為服<pc>。</pc>
