</div>
<div>
<p>
<persName>舒亶</persName>
<pc>，</pc>字<name key="舒亶" type="zi">信道</name>
<pc>，</pc>
<placeName>明州</placeName>慈溪人<pc>。</pc>試禮部第<num value="1">一</num>
